+      description: Use neoadjuvant chemotherapy as the treatment of choice for inflammatory breast cancer or unresectable locally advanced disease that may become resectable.
+      kind: MedicationRequest
+      evidence_traceability_ids: [claim-r1-1]
+      provenance:
+        source: source_direct
+    - id: use-standard-tumor-features
+      label: Use histology grade stage and receptor status to guide decisions
+      description: Use tumor histology, grade, stage, and ER PR HER2 expression to guide the decision to pursue neoadjuvant chemotherapy.
