+      label: Neoadjuvant breast cancer treatment pathway
+      description: Overall pathway for evaluating, selecting, and monitoring neoadjuvant systemic therapy in invasive nonmetastatic breast cancer.
+      actor: multidisciplinary oncology team
+    - id: candidacy-phase
+      label: Candidacy and treatment intent
+      description: Determine whether neoadjuvant therapy is indicated and what clinical goal it serves.
