codex
The generated PlanDefinitions are referencing 15 named CQL identifiers, so the library has to match those names exactly. I’m writing a mixed retrieve-plus-parameter CQL library now: subtype and response logic come from formalized value sets, while context-heavy guideline judgments stay explicit as boolean inputs instead of pretending the source gave computable EHR criteria that it didn’t.
apply patch
