+    - id: de-inflammatory-stage
+      condition_id: inflammatory-or-locally-advanced
+      label: Clinical stage and resectability assessment
+      description: Review inflammatory presentation, local extent, and initial surgical resectability.
+      data_type: diagnosis
+    - id: de-residual-disease-impact
+      condition_id: residual-disease-would-change-adjuvant-therapy
+      label: Potential adjuvant treatment change
+      description: Determine whether residual disease findings would alter adjuvant treatment recommendations.
+      data_type: assessment
+    - id: de-local-therapy-goal
+      condition_id: local-therapy-downstaging-goal
+      label: Local therapy reduction goal
+      description: Document whether the intent is to increase breast conservation or reduce axillary surgery.
+      data_type: patient-reported
+    - id: de-surgery-delay
+      condition_id: surgery-delay-context
+      label: Surgical timing constraints
+      description: Document decision-making, testing, or reconstruction factors that justify delay in surgery.
