+    - id: offer-postmenopausal-neoadjuvant-endocrine-therapy
+      label: Offer aromatase inhibitor based neoadjuvant endocrine therapy for postmenopausal downstaging
+      description: Use neoadjuvant endocrine therapy with an aromatase inhibitor in postmenopausal HR-positive HER2-negative disease to increase locoregional treatment options.
+      kind: MedicationRequest
+      evidence_traceability_ids: [claim-r4-2]
+      provenance:
+        source: source_direct
+    - id: use-endocrine-therapy-for-disease-control
+      label: Use endocrine therapy for disease control when surgery is not planned
+      description: Use endocrine therapy for disease control if there is no intent to proceed to surgery.
+      kind: MedicationRequest
+      evidence_traceability_ids: [claim-r4-2]
+      provenance:
+        source: source_direct
+    - id: avoid-premenopausal-neoadjuvant-endocrine-therapy
+      label: Do not routinely offer neoadjuvant endocrine therapy to premenopausal patients
+      description: Avoid routine neoadjuvant endocrine therapy outside a clinical trial in premenopausal HR-positive HER2-negative early-stage disease.
+      kind: MedicationRequest
+      do_not_perform: true
+      evidence_traceability_ids: [claim-r4-3]
+      provenance:
