One concrete follow-up remains if you care about publishable canonicals rather than local validation: [formalize-config.yaml](/Users/taylorkingston/rh-skills-projects/asco-cancer-guideline/topics/asco-breast-cancer-guideline/process/formalize-config.yaml) is using the default base URL `http://example.org/fhir`.
